definitions.definition: Annoyingly or disappointingly bad , in various senses; lousy , corny , cringy , uncool , messed up .
examples: Every record they ever made was straight-up wack .

main_definition: ( originally African-American Vernacular , slang ) Annoyingly or disappointingly bad , in various senses; lousy , corny , cringy , uncool , messed up .
